# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:23
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "और जानें"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:24
msgid ""
"We are working hard to expand this user guide and to improve OpenShot Video "
"Editor, but if you are stuck and don't know where to turn, OpenShot has "
"several sources for additional information."
msgstr ""
"हम इस उपयोगकर्ता मार्गदर्शिका का विस्तार करने और OpenShot Video Editor को बेहतर "
"बनाने के लिए कड़ी मेहनत कर रहे हैं, लेकिन यदि आप फंस गए हैं और नहीं जानते कि कहाँ जाएं, तो "
"OpenShot के पास अतिरिक्त जानकारी के लिए कई स्रोत हैं।"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:27
msgid ""
"OpenShot has several `YouTube Tutorials <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ available to help you learn more."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot के पास आपकी सहायता के लिए कई `YouTube ट्यूटोरियल्स <https://www.youtube."
"com/playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ उपलब्ध हैं।"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:28
msgid ""
"OpenShot has a `Reddit User Community <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedicated to users helping users, answering questions, and discussing video "
"editing and OpenShot topics."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot के पास एक `Reddit उपयोगकर्ता समुदाय <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ है "
"जो उपयोगकर्ताओं की मदद करने, प्रश्नों का उत्तर देने, और वीडियो संपादन तथा OpenShot "
"विषयों पर चर्चा करने के लिए समर्पित है।"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you would like to help improve this User Guide, `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."
msgstr ""
"यदि आप इस उपयोगकर्ता मार्गदर्शिका को बेहतर बनाने में मदद करना चाहते हैं, तो `GitHub पर "
"स्रोत देखें <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_।"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you have discovered a new bug, please `Report a Bug <https://www.openshot."
"org/issues/new/>`_."
msgstr ""
"यदि आपने कोई नया बग पाया है, तो कृपया `बग रिपोर्ट करें <https://www.openshot.org/"
"issues/new/>`_।"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you need professional support, you can open a ticket by sending an "
"message to support@openshot.org or `Schedule a call <https://calendly.com/"
"openshot-support/desktop>`_."
msgstr ""
"यदि आपको पेशेवर सहायता की आवश्यकता है, तो आप support@openshot.org पर संदेश भेजकर "
"टिकट खोल सकते हैं या `कॉल शेड्यूल करें <https://calendly.com/openshot-support/"
"desktop>`_।"
